{"tid":879852,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"尚悅．嶺暫收150票 最快周二加推","createTime":"2018-10-28T10:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T11:01:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5dde44194f0840a691c161ff19277140d6a8ca1a","tid":879852,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"恒地(00012)及新世界(00017)旗下元朗尚悅．嶺昨日首度開放示範單位及收票，恒基物業代理營業(一)部總經理林達民表示，截至今天共收到約150張入票，較首批101伙，已錄足額認購。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，昨天樓盤展銷廳錄約4500人次參觀，今天截至下午約3時半，亦已有2000多人次參觀。由於日前同區另一新盤首輪開售，他對參觀情況已感到滿意。<br />\n<br />\n他說，項目最快周二(30日)加推單位應市，預料按原定計劃首輪推售最少152伙，暫定11月初揀樓。<br />\n<br />\n尚悅．嶺位於元朗大棠路99A號，由兩座25層住宅組成，共提供504伙，實用面積174至381方呎，預計關鍵日期2020年9月30日。"},{"pid":"54bf26cf2d99831511543909efcffba9bdfd93ab","tid":879852,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"超級星期日收50張飛 即25人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387391a9755484405627635c42b3e69e86e173f8","tid":879852,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"收得150票都加推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bd5f70181121eb86d8cd8c22c7c57d63d599e0","tid":879852,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"919d3469b1131fe924cf56397972258453174b46","tid":879852,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"4叔份interim本身已經麻麻<br />\n睇黎份Final死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a4a4a55fd1f95f3c79c99ba4385be19929085f","tid":879852,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"919d3469b1131fe924cf56397972258453174b46","tid":879852,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"4叔份interim本身已經麻麻<br />\n睇黎份Final死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c